#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:5
msgid "Continue installation remotely using SSH"
msgstr "Mynd ymlaen gyda'r sefydliad o bell gan ddefnyddio SSH"

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#: ../network-console.templates:9
msgid "Start menu, Start shell"
msgstr "Cychwyn dewislen, Cychwyn plisgyn"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:11
msgid "Network console option:"
msgstr "Opsiwn consol rhwydwaith:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:11
msgid ""
"This is the network console for the Debian installer. From here, you may "
"start the Debian installer main menu, or execute an interactive shell."
msgstr ""
"Dyma'r consol rhwydwaith ar gyfer y sefydlydd Debian. O fan yma, gallwch "
"gychwyn prif ddewislen y sefydlydd Debian, neu gychwyn plisgyn rhyngweithiol."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:11
msgid "To return to this menu, you will need to log in again."
msgstr "Er mwyn dychwelyd i'r ddewislen hon, bydd rhaid i chi fewngofnodi eto."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:20
msgid "Generating SSH host key"
msgstr "Yn cynhyrchu allwedd gwesteiwr SSH"

#. Type: password
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:24
msgid "Remote installation password:"
msgstr "Cyfrinair sefydliad pell:"

#. Type: password
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:24
msgid ""
"You need to set a password for remote access to the Debian installer. A "
"malicious or unqualified user with access to the installer can have "
"disastrous results, so you should take care to choose a password that is not "
"easy to guess. It should not be a word found in the dictionary, or a word "
"that could be easily associated with you, like your middle name."
msgstr ""
"Rhaid i chi osod cyfrinair ar gyfer mynediad pell i'r sefydlydd Debian. Gall "
"ddefnyddiwr maleisus neu anghymwys gyda mynediad i'r sefydlydd achosi "
"canlyniadau trychinebus, felly dylech gymryd gofal i ddewis cyfrinair nad "
"yw'n hawdd i'w ddyfalu. Ni ddylai fod yn air a geir mewn geriradir, neu'n "
"air a ellir ei gysylltu'n hawdd a chi, fel eich enw canol."

#. Type: password
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:24
msgid ""
"This password is used only by the Debian installer, and will be discarded "
"once you finished the installation."
msgstr ""
"Defnyddir y cyfrinair hwn gan sefydlydd Debian yn unig, a caiff ei waredu "
"unwaith rydych chi wedi gorffen y sefydliad."

#. Type: password
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:37
msgid "Password confirmation:"
msgstr "Cadarnhad cyfrinair:"

#. Type: password
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:37
msgid ""
"Please enter the same remote installation password again to verify that you "
"have typed it correctly."
msgstr ""
"Rhowch yr un cyfrinair sefydliad pell eto er mwyn gwirio eich bod chi wedi "
"ei deipio'n gywir."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:43
msgid "Password empty"
msgstr "Cyfrinair gwag"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:43
msgid ""
"You seem to have entered an empty remote installation password. That is not "
"secure. Please enter a password again."
msgstr ""
"Ymddengys eich bod chi wedi rhoi cyfrinair sefydliad pell gwag. Nid yw hyn "
"yn ddiogel. Rhowch gyfrinair eto."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:49
msgid "Password mismatch"
msgstr "Cyfrineiriau gwahanol"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:49
msgid ""
"The two passwords you entered were not the same. Please enter a password "
"again."
msgstr "Nid yw'r ddau gyfrinair a rhoddoch yr un peth. Rhowch gyfrinair eto."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:55
msgid "Finish the installation"
msgstr "Gorffen y sefydliad"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:55
msgid ""
"To finish the installation, please start the newly installed system and use "
"an SSH client to log in as the \"installer\" user."
msgstr ""
"Er mwyn gorffen y sefydliad, cychwynwch y system newydd ei sefydlu a "
"defnyddiwch gleient SSH i fewngofnodi fel y defnyddiwr \"installer\"."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:61
msgid "Start SSH"
msgstr "Cychwyn SSH"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:61
msgid ""
"To continue the installation, please use an SSH client to log in as the "
"\"installer\" user."
msgstr ""
"Er mwyn mynd ymlaen gyda'r sefydliad, defnyddiwch gleient SSH i fewngofnodi "
"fel y defnyddiwr \"installer\"."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:61
msgid "The fingerprint of this SSH server's host key is: ${fingerprint}"
msgstr "Dyma ôl bys allwedd gwesteiwr y gweinydd SSH yma: ${fingerprint}"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../network-console.templates:61
msgid ""
"Please check this carefully against the fingerprint reported by your SSH "
"client."
msgstr ""
"Gwiriwch ywn yn ofalus yn erbyn yr ôl bys a adroddir gan eich cleient SSH."
